http://url.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-url-password

----
instance.host : String

The host of the current Location. Composed of 
%%#hostname|**hostname**%%
and %%#port|**port**%% (if any).

<htmlexample>
<script>
  console.log(window.location.host);
</script>
</htmlexample>

